<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h3>Welcome to Report It!</h3>
    <p>Hi, <%= @user.first_name %></p>
    <p>
      You have successfully signed up to Report It!
    </p>
    <p>
      Your username is the email address where you received this email.
    </p>
    <p>
      To get started, we need you to activate your account. To do so simply click <%= link_to 'here', @url %>
      <br />
      <small>(We make you jump through a couple of hoops, but it's worth it for the additional security of your account.)</small>
    </p>
    <p>
      After activating, you will be automatically logged in.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for joining and have a great day!</p>
    <p>Sincerely,</p>
    <p>The Report It! team</p>
  </body>
</html>